title:	contact
desc:	How to contact us.

body:
<h2>e-mail</h2>
<p>There are multiple e-mail accounts <em>&at;rsget.pl</em>. You can find most
	of them in appropriate <a href="/about/">about</a> sections.</p>

<h2>IRC</h2>
<dl>
	<dt>server</dt>
	<dd>irc.freenode.net (<a href="http://freenode.net/">web</a>)</dd>

	<dt>channel</dt>
	<dd>#rsget.pl</dd>

	<dt>note</dt>
	<dd>I (sparky) use nickname SamChi at freenode,
		because sparky was used already.</dd>

	<dt>rules</dt>
	<dd>Say hi, ask your query and stay until someone answers you.</dd>

	<dt>webchat</dt>
	<dd><a href="http://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=rsget.pl">quick link</a></dd>
</dl>

<h2>other ?</h2>
<p>If you think there should be another way to contact developer(s)
	and other users let us know. The possibilities are:</p>
<ul>
	<li>forum</li>
	<li>mailing list</li>
	<li>comments on this web page</li>
</ul>
